CCTV footage has emerged showing a man hijacked by two armed men outside 22 Gardenia Road in Pinetown, KwaZulu-Natal. The video below contains footage from two different camera angles. The first half of the video shows the men arriving and another resident pulling into the road, Highway Mail reported. The driver of the other vehicle notices the men in masks and quickly speeds off. The second portion of the footage, which starts at the 1.45 marks, shows the hijacking taking place. The hijack victim is seen waiting at an intercom when two armed men appear at his window. &#8211; Caxton News Service For more news your way, follow The Citizen on Facebook and Twitter .